{"word":"G4818 - συλλυπέω - syllypéō - sool-loop-eh'-o - Be grieved","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συλλυπέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">syllypéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sool-loop-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be grieved</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விசனப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to affect with grief together"},{"paragraph":"2. to grieve with oneself"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G3076 - λυπέω - lypéō - loo-peh'-o/3076\">G3076</a>; to <i>afflict jointly</i>, that is, (passively) <i>sorrow at</i> (on account of) some one: - be grieved.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G253/253\">G253</a>, <a href=\"#/G3076/3076\">G3076</a>, <a href=\"#/G3077/3077\">G3077</a>, <a href=\"#/G4036/4036\">G4036</a>, <a href=\"#/G4818/4818\">G4818</a>"}]}